ding required for leadership in today's world. Arts Arts Fact Sheet Arts Website Biological Sciences Biological Sciences Fact Sheet Biological Sciences Website Business Business Fact Sheet Business Website Education Education Fact Sheet Education Website Engineering Engineering Fact Sheet Engineering Website Humanities Humanities Fact Sheet Humanities Website Information & Computer Sciences Information & Computer Sciences Fact Sheet Information & Computer Sciences Website Interdisciplinary Studies Interdisciplinary Studies Website Law Law Fact Sheet Law Website Physical Sciences Physical Sciences Fact Sheet Physical Sciences Website Social Ecology Social Ecology Fact Sheet Social Ecology Website Social Sciences Social Sciences Fact Sheet Social Sciences Website Susan and Henry Samueli College of Health Sciences In September 2017, UCI announced that Orange County philanthropists and business leaders Susan and Henry Samueli committed $200 million to name its College of Health Sciences and establish a new integrative health research institute. The college consists of the School of Medicine, the Sue and Bill Gross School of Nursing, the School of Pharmacy (currently the Department of Pharmaceutical Sciences) and the School of Population Health (currently the Program in Public Health.) At the college’s core is the Susan Samueli Integrative Health Institute. Learn more here. Medicine Medicine Fact Sheet Medicine Website Nursing Nursing Fact Sheet Nursing Website Pharmaceutical Sciences Pharmaceutical Sciences Fact Sheet Pharmaceutical Sciences Website Public Health Public Health Fact Sheet Public Health Website Related Links Office of the Provost & Executive Vice Chancellor General Catalogue List of Majors & Minors Schedule of Classes Undergraduate/Undeclared Division of Undergraduate Education Graduate Division Division of Continuing Education Campuswide Honors Program Undergraduate Research UCI CalTeach Libraries Study Abroad Center Summer Session Academic Calendars Aca